data.value:
You're eligible for a Genius discount at Serenity Lodge! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in. Set in Sharm El Sheikh, 300 metres from White Knight Bay Beach, Serenity Lodge offers accommodation with a private beach area , free private parking, pool with a view and a bar. The property has sea views and is 600 metres from Ras Nasrani Beach and 1.9 km from SOHO Square Sharm El Sheikh . The bed and breakfast features family rooms.
At the bed and breakfast, every unit has a desk. With a private bathroom equipped with a bath, units at the bed and breakfast also have free WiFi, while some rooms come with a balcony. At the bed and breakfast, the units come with bed linen and towels.
